snippet.title: Guitar Hero: Warriors of Rock Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: In Guitar Hero: Warriors of Rock, join with friends on an epic rock journey to save rock n' roll.  Featuring an impressive 90+ track set list and a host of all-new gameplay features, living room legends and their friends can strum, drum and wail in the most immersive music videogame experience to date.
